# 写在前面
参考了[【尚硅谷】数据结构与算法（Java数据结构与算法）](https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1E4411H73v?t=1.2)
以及[数据结构与算法基础（青岛大学-王卓）](https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1nJ411V7bd?t=1.0)

后者的算法思路讲解更加清晰，而前者的代码实现更加详细，最好两边都看一下加深理解。非常感谢这两位老师！
算法思想在网上已经有非常多讲解了，在此就不再赘述，直接放代码。

使用java进行实现，假设结点数据类型为char，边的权重数据类型为int，以0索引的顶点开始构造最小生成树
代码文件一共有两个，分别是定义了MGraph对象的MGraph.java和作为主函数的PrimTest.java
在MGraph类中的成员方法prim()实现了构造无向图最小生成树，并将最小生成树的每条边及其权重在控制台中输出。

代码新手，如有不足还请海涵。

# 作为例子的无向图
![无向图](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GardenKitten/Picbed/main/blog_files/img/mstree1.jpg)

# 代码实现
## MGraph.java
```java
public class MGraph {
    private int vertexNum;//结点数
    private char[] vertexData;//结点数据
    private int[][] weight;//边的权重
    static final int INFINITE = Integer.MAX_VALUE;//将int最大值看作无穷大

    public MGraph(int vertexNum, char[] vertexData, int[][] weight) {
        this.vertexNum = vertexNum;
        this.weight = weight;
        this.vertexData = new char[vertexNum];//赋值前一定要先初始化

        for (int i = 0; i < vertexNum; i++) {
            this.vertexData[i] = vertexData[i];
            for (int j = 0; j < vertexNum; j++) {
                this.weight[i][j] = weight[i][j];
            }
        }
    }

    /**
     * @param startVerx 开始构建最小生成树的顶点的下标
     */
    void prim(int startVerx) {
        //记录结点是否已被收入最小生成树，默认初始值为false
        boolean[] contains = new boolean[vertexNum];
        //将开始顶点标记为已收入
        contains[startVerx] = true;

        //记录一条边的两个结点下标
        //v1为已收入的结点，v2为未收入的结点
        int v1 = -1, v2 = -1;
        int minWeight = INFINITE;//初始化为“无限大”


        //遍历一次找到一条符合条件的边
        //最小生成树中有“顶点数-1”条边，所以从1开始遍历
        for (int k = 1; k < vertexNum; k++) {
            //遍历已被收入的边
            for (int i = 0; i < vertexNum; i++) {
                //遍历未被收入的边
                for (int j = 0; j < vertexNum; j++) {
                    //如果找到最小边，就修改minWeight的值并记录顶点
                    //contains[i] && !contains[j]: 防止出现回路
                    if (contains[i] && !contains[j] && weight[i][j] < minWeight) {
                        minWeight = weight[i][j];
                        v1 = i;
                        v2 = j;
                    }
                }
            }
            //如果遍历了整个邻接矩阵仍未找到符合要求的边，说明该图不连通
            //此时退出循环并报错
            if (minWeight == INFINITE) {
                System.out.println("该图不连通，无法构造最小生成树！");
                break;
            }

            //打印已找到的边
            System.out.println("(" + vertexData[v1] + "," + vertexData[v2] + ") " + minWeight);
            //重置minWeight
            minWeight = INFINITE;
            //将v2也收入到最小生成树中
            contains[v2]=true;
        }
    }

    //--getter and setter--

    public int getVertexNum() {
        return vertexNum;
    }

    public void setVertexNum(int vertexNum) {
        this.vertexNum = vertexNum;
    }

    public char[] getVertexData() {
        return vertexData;
    }

    public void setVertexData(char[] vertexData) {
        for (int i = 0; i < vertexNum; i++) {
            this.vertexData[i] = vertexData[i];
        }
    }

    public int[][] getWeight() {
        return weight;
    }

    public void setWeight(int[][] weight) {
        for (int i = 0; i < vertexNum; i++)
            for (int j = 0; j < vertexNum; j++)
                this.weight[i][j] = weight[i][j];
    }
}

```

## PrimTest.java
```java
public class PrimTest {
    //将int最大值看作无穷大

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        char[] data = {'A', 'B', 'C', 'D', 'E', 'F'};
        int[][] weight = new int[][]{
                {0, 6, 1, 5, MGraph.INFINITE, MGraph.INFINITE},
                {6, 0, 5, MGraph.INFINITE, 3, MGraph.INFINITE},
                {1, 5, 0, 5, 6, 4},
                {5, MGraph.INFINITE, 5, 0, MGraph.INFINITE, 2},
                {MGraph.INFINITE, 3, 6, MGraph.INFINITE, 0, 6},
                {MGraph.INFINITE, MGraph.INFINITE, 4, 2, 6, 0}
        };

        MGraph graph = new MGraph(data.length, data, weight);
        graph.prim(0);
    }
}
```

# 运行结果
>(A,C) 1
>(C,F) 4
>(F,D) 2
>(C,B) 5
>(B,E) 3

